 &lt;p&gt;⭐️⭐️⭐️&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://leetcode.com/problems/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock-with-transaction-fee/&#34;&gt;&lt;ins class=&#34;dot&#34;&gt;題目敘述&lt;/ins&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are given an array  &lt;code&gt;prices&lt;/code&gt;  where  &lt;code&gt;prices[i]&lt;/code&gt;  is the price of a given stock on the  &lt;code&gt;ith&lt;/code&gt;  day, and an integer  &lt;code&gt;fee&lt;/code&gt;  representing a transaction fee.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Find the maximum profit you can achieve. You may complete as many transactions as you like, but you need to pay the transaction fee for each transaction.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; You may not engage in multiple transactions simultaneously (i.e., you must sell the stock before you buy again).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;example-1&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#example-1&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Example 1&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Input&lt;/strong&gt;: prices = [1,3,2,8,4,9], fee = 2&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Output&lt;/strong&gt;: 8&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Explanation&lt;/strong&gt;: The maximum profit can be achieved by:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Buying at prices[0] = 1&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Selling at prices[3] = 8&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Buying at prices[4] = 4&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Selling at prices[5] = 9&lt;br /&gt;
The total profit is ((8 - 1) - 2) + ((9 - 4) - 2) = 8.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;example-2&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#example-2&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Example 2&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Input&lt;/strong&gt;: prices = [1,3,7,5,10,3], fee = 3&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Output&lt;/strong&gt;: 6&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;解題思路&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#解題思路&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 解題思路&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;solution&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#solution&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Solution&lt;/h2&gt;
