          &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;item&#34; title=&#34;Bowen&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl image&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9tZWRpdW0uY29tL2ktdGhpbmstc28taS1saXZlL2dpdCVFNCVCOCU4QSVFNyU5QSU4NCVFNCVCOCU4OSVFNyVBOCVBRSVFNSVCNyVBNSVFNCVCRCU5QyVFNiVCNSU4MSVFNyVBOCU4Qi0xMGY0ZjkxNTE2N2U=&#34; data-background-image=&#34;https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/5968/5968906.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
